Summary: Biochemical reaction from ospemifene to ospemifene carboxylic acid.
Biochemical reaction from ospemifene to 4-hydroxyospemifene. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2B6, CYP2C9, CYP2C19 or CYP3A4.
Biochemical reaction from ospemifene to 4'-hydroxyospemifene. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP3A5 or CYP3A4.
